{"tid":1524752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"901 塞機場必勝法 / 一人一uber 排隊入東涌","createTime":"2019-08-31T18:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:26:27.000Z","uid":253170,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"69dfcccf0309f0b177b53be47c4cb04c7a8fa14c","tid":1524752,"uid":253170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f811f5705f336cab576c95b107f2b754d6cc8a","tid":1524752,"uid":253170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />塞撚爆佢"},{"pid":"2a756ccae3f2994cb52b9f0a35d174ad2bd47557","tid":1524752,"uid":228934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:07:45.000Z","msg":"有人性嘅應該劈炮唔好做 cctvb<br />\n我心裡梗係想佢係因良心發現而辭職啦<br />\n佢係鬼良心發現辭職咩<br />\n係比班同事投訴佢番工唔做野掛住化妝<br />\n覺得比人杯先辭渣<br />\n仲帶哂光環咁<br />\n又墊pad又重機心<br />\n屋企警察世家攞咩光環<br />\n<br />\n利申：見過素顏唔會想j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前提係 一個報cctvb假新聞主播 連登仔都撐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n精蟲上腦<br />\n<br />\n只能說 3毛已帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔新標準<br />\nPopo或tvb主播只要肯辭職就原諒<br />\n咁獨立調查委員會都唔需要了<br />\n<br />\n大和解 super<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大和解 完啦 過主啦<br />\n大和解 完啦 過主啦 祝佢一家做政府 升多幾級 秉持著喺tvb做咗咁多年是是旦旦偏頗打壓式工作態度 fighting <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我叫各位了解清楚記者主播離職原因先好讚，唔好以為依家辭職一定同新聞審查有關，見人哋大波就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。金盈係被人屌走加佢條仔冇得升職兼唔撈。<br />\n梁凱寧五年前柒犬有聯署，佢係有良心當時已經走。<br />\n<br />\n佢仲要做足7年做到2019 年，想洗白，叫3毛開post造勢，直入海關警察入境<br />\n恭喜 各大紀律部隊都成功染紅呀 cctvb全面進場<br />\n當年有份聯署既人，大部分都走哂<br />\n<br />\n依家仲留得係度既人，你都估到佢係咩人？？？？"},{"pid":"579c37396f8d09b1fec6e96715fed106b33d7aa4","tid":1524752,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:08:18.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"399a762fc8e60212d7e45cd5da71373df4157979","tid":1524752,"uid":253170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:09:33.000Z","msg":"如果係的士塞車塞到唔耐煩<br />\n其實可以即刻落車㗎<br />\n(注意落車位置安全）<br />\n<br />\nby 一個好賤既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba81a7f9788fd71b27728fccb3e870023bb685a","tid":1524752,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:10:11.000Z","msg":"推阿"},{"pid":"c889ac2cb0c2fa8a9ba60353caf7d28b90b95375","tid":1524752,"uid":266081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:10:45.000Z","msg":"唔搭UBER都可以去東涌線同機鐵站排隊同詢問<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1524751/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1524751/page/1</a><br />\n[活動指南] 機場和你飛行動，作為和理非可以有咩活動呢？"},{"pid":"5b982932ccebf575d479f07572e7d7302b70f504","tid":1524752,"uid":253170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:10:51.000Z","msg":"塞到佢停飛就好完啦<br />\n<br />\n讓返條路比機場啲手足走"},{"pid":"20083657e801a3aada4c8410ca81d2c656fd0d4f","tid":1524752,"uid":214508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:11:28.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"47f1674795d8de8e7fcb54ff6c7854d9cece2dc7","tid":1524752,"uid":214508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:11:38.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"72a07b0ce76afa66005c605f69e62861c65e85e9","tid":1524752,"uid":214508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:11:54.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"abf1b7e0a0ec4991da01808388a8418798f53cb6","tid":1524752